When I saw the message, I told 
Concubine Lihua about it, as well.

257
00:19:51,030 --> 00:19:55,000
But it seemed like everything 
I said only made her believe me less.

258
00:19:56,450 --> 00:19:57,780
So...

259
00:19:59,300 --> 00:20:02,760
What can I do for you?

260
00:20:09,560 --> 00:20:12,940
Well, starting today, you'll 
be my lady-in-waiting!

261
00:20:14,150 --> 00:20:15,210
Huh?

262
00:20:16,590 --> 00:20:19,020
<i>There are some things Maomao cannot hold back.</i>

263
00:20:19,020 --> 00:20:22,060
<i>Curiosity, a thirst for knowledge...</i>

264
00:20:22,060 --> 00:20:25,870
<i>And just a smidgen of a sense of justice.</i>

265
00:20:30,270 --> 00:20:34,260
No, no, no, no...

266
00:20:34,260 --> 00:20:37,630
No, if I keep a low profile, 
it shouldn't matter where Iâ€”

267
00:20:34,750 --> 00:20:36,210
Hey, Maomao!

268
00:20:36,210 --> 00:20:39,390
Welcome back, Maomao! How was it?

269
00:20:39,840 --> 00:20:44,520
<i>And thus, Maomao became a
 lady-in-waiting of Concubine Gyokuyou,</i>

270
00:20:44,520 --> 00:20:46,900
<i>recipient of the emperor's love.</i>

271
00:20:46,900 --> 00:20:49,810
<i>Put simply, it was a big promotion.</i>

272
00:20:57,980 --> 00:20:59,570
Hey!

